Assure vs Ensure

Meaning-  The word ‘assure’ is used to commit to someone that something will happen for sure or will be true, so as to remove doubts and confusion. 
On the contrary, 'ensure' is a verb, which can be used in situations when we make sure that something will or will not happen.

Example-   The doctor assured us that there would be no complications.
                      - Please ensure that there is no loophole.
